<TEXT>
<P>
	Stocks Lower; Dow Down 89.34  
</P>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Prices were mixed on Wall Street today after  
analysts found data in the government's latest economic assessment 
that rekindled inflation fears. At the close on Wall Street, the 
Dow Jones industrial average was down 89.34 at 10,789.04. Losers on 
the NYSE led gainers 1,665-1,339. The Nasdaq was up 14.44 at 
2,542.88. 

